        <p style="font-size:1rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.6);line-height:1.8;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Founded by Sutton Huggins, an MMA fighter and advocate for health and fitness, Ascend Performance Nutrition was born out of a desire to offer athletes supplements that are not only effective but also clean and natural.</p>
