        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Selfless leadership at home. Training supports your calling, never replaces it.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#06A5C5;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Selfless leadership</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#06A5C5;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Home first</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#06A5C5;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Support, not replacement</li>
        </ul>
      </div>

      <!-- America -->
      <div class="value-card">
        <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1;">&#127482;&#127480;</div>
        <h3 style="font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#f0ede8;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">America</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Gratitude, service, and respect for those who protect our freedom.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#06A5C5;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Gratitude for freedom</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#06A5C5;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Service to others</li>
          <li style="font-size:0.8125rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.35);display:flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;"><span style="color:#06A5C5;font-size:0.625rem;">&#9679;</span>Honor those who protect</li>
        </ul>
