        <div style="font-size:2rem;margin-bottom:1.25rem;line-height:1;">&#128170;</div>
        <h3 style="font-family:Georgia,serif;font-size:1.25rem;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:-0.01em;color:#f0ede8;margin-bottom:0.75rem;">Fitness</h3>
        <p style="font-size:0.875rem;color:rgba(255,255,255,0.45);line-height:1.7;margin-bottom:1.25rem;">Stewardship of the body through smart training, clean supplements, and hard recovery.</p>
        <ul style="list-style:none;display:flex;flex-direction:column;gap:0.5rem;">
